## Example 1: Simple prematch decoder
Log: wazuh: Agent buffer: '192.168.1.1'
```xml
<decoder name="wazuh">
  <prematch>^wazuh: </prematch>
</decoder>
<decoder name="agent-buffer">
  <parent>wazuh</parent>
  <prematch offset="after_parent">^Agent buffer:</prematch>
  <regex offset="after_prematch">^ '(\S+)'.</regex>
  <order>level</order>
</decoder>
```

